1
00:00:48,119 --> 00:00:48,960
This New Year's Eve dinner...

2
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:49,399
Xiaoyong,

3
00:00:49,399 --> 00:00:50,439
you've got to eat plenty, okay?

4
00:00:50,439 --> 00:00:50,799
Here.

5
00:00:51,039 --> 00:00:51,560
Have some.

6
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:52,280
Come on.

7
00:00:52,439 --> 00:00:53,000
Eat up.

8
00:00:54,159 --> 00:00:54,679
It's delicious.

9
00:00:54,759 --> 00:00:55,560
Tasty, isn't it?

10
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:56,280
Good, right?

11
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:57,520
Mom made this just for you.

12
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,280
Try these dumplings.

13
00:00:58,280 --> 00:00:59,320
Your mom made them too.

14
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:00,799
Go on, try them.

15
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:02,759
Look at this.

16
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,640
The Spring Festival Gala this year...

17
00:01:04,799 --> 00:01:05,719
It's the same every year.

18
00:01:05,719 --> 00:01:06,760
So hilarious.

19
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:09,120
Dad, Mom,

20
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,239
tonight,

21
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,719
Team China has a football match.

22
00:01:13,159 --> 00:01:13,719
I want to watch it.

23
00:01:14,079 --> 00:01:14,760
Xiaoyong,

24
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,719
your dad, you know,

25
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,159
his heart isn't great.

26
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,719
Football matches like this,

27
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:21,079
they get him too worked up.

28
00:01:21,359 --> 00:01:21,920
How about

29
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:23,359
we just skip it tonight?

30
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:25,719
Xiaoyong,

31
00:01:26,239 --> 00:01:27,120
listen to Mom, okay?

32
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:28,280
I made so much good food.

33
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:30,040
Just sit down and enjoy it.

34
00:01:30,439 --> 00:01:31,680
Listen to your mom.

35
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,359
Eat, eat up, come on.

36
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:34,560
Eat, eat, have plenty.

37
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:36,640
Here.

38
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,159
Have some more.

39
00:01:39,359 --> 00:01:40,200
Try Mom's cooking.

40
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:40,799
How is it?

41
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,280
Delicious.

42
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,079
On the team, we've noticed Zhou Hang

43
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,680
likes to show off to his teammates.

44
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:55,079
"My girlfriend bought me this,"

45
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,560
"and she bought me this too."

46
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:57,920
You really support him.

47
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,400
Of course I support him.

48
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,680
You have no idea

49
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,200
just how much I support him,

50
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,200
how much I love him.

51
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,680
The way he looks on the pitch

52
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,400
is so handsome.

53
00:02:05,599 --> 00:02:07,040
Especially when he's shouting,

54
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:08,719
he's so manly.

55
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,120
Anyway,

56
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,319
he loves football,

57
00:02:11,439 --> 00:02:12,680
and I love him for loving football.

58
00:02:12,879 --> 00:02:14,199
If you had to use one sentence

59
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,319
to describe him,

60
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:16,120
what would you say?

61
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,199
He...

62
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,919
He's just

63
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,560
a big kid who loves football.

64
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,039
He's played since he was little,

65
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,000
and grew up to be a PE teacher.

66
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:24,800
Very pure-hearted.

67
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:26,039
When he's under a lot of pressure,

68
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,520
have you noticed any

69
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:28,680
changes in him?

70
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,840
He's been talking less lately.

71
00:02:31,159 --> 00:02:32,400
Bottling it up.

72
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:34,400
I often see him in a corner

73
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:36,039
watching match videos,

74
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,520
studying them,

75
00:02:37,759 --> 00:02:39,439
figuring out how to score a goal,

76
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,599
how to get a point,

77
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,560
how to win a match.

78
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,719
He works so hard.

79
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,159
Since the season began,

80
00:02:44,439 --> 00:02:45,560
we've seen Donglin lose weight,

81
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,639
over ten pounds.

82
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:47,879
It must hurt to see that.

83
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:50,080
This kid, ever since he was little,

84
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:51,560
only shares the good news.

85
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:53,439
But I see on TV

86
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,159
he's always falling down,

87
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,759
getting tackled by others.

88
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:59,319
Then at home, he secretly

89
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:00,439
rubs ointment on himself.

90
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:01,560
In the middle of the night,

91
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,039
he's still training at home.

92
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,840
I told him to sleep earlier,

93
00:03:05,439 --> 00:03:06,319
and he said,

94
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:08,439
"When you're bad, you've got to practice more."

95
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:10,639
So will you continue to support him

96
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:11,280
in playing football?

97
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:13,000
I'm fairly supportive of him playing,

98
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:16,280
but going pro is a tough road.

99
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:19,199
Xiaoxiao should be 17 this year,

100
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:21,159
the youngest on the whole team.

101
00:03:21,639 --> 00:03:23,199
Do you have plans for his future?

102
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,639
Whether it's the college entrance exam or going pro,

103
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,039
whatever his decision is,

104
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:28,240
I'll support him.

105
00:03:28,599 --> 00:03:29,280
As family members,

106
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,280
have you talked

107
00:03:30,319 --> 00:03:31,039
with the other players' family members

108
00:03:31,039 --> 00:03:31,840
together about this?

109
00:03:32,159 --> 00:03:32,719
Like when they're

110
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:33,759
under a lot of pressure,

111
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:35,120
what ways do you have

112
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,280
to help them relieve it?

113
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:38,039
We have discussed this issue.

114
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,000
But when it comes to playing,

115
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:40,719
to the matches,

116
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:42,039
there's obviously nothing we can do to help.

117
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,719
But the one thing we can do

118
00:03:43,719 --> 00:03:45,560
is to be their strongest support.

119
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:47,280
Did Daddy give this to you?

120
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,319
Daddy looks handsome when he plays, right?

121
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:54,080
The child isn't very talkative,

122
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:56,039
but when she's at school,

123
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:58,759
some kids know her dad

124
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,719
plays football.

125
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,240
Some kids

126
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:02,439
have made fun of her,

127
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,360
but most of the kids

128
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,280
are kind about it.

129
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,080
Her dad also said

130
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:08,599
he absolutely has to

131
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:09,680
win a match for his kid.

132
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,960
I really hope that promise

133
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,680
can come true.

134
00:04:14,719 --> 00:04:15,159
Looking forward to it.

135
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,920
If you had to use one sentence

136
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:20,040
to sum up Mr. Xie,

137
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,360
what would you say?

138
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,959
He's just an ordinary guy.

139
00:04:32,639 --> 00:04:33,680
All right, stop watching.

140
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,759
Hurry and eat, it's getting cold.

141
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:35,519
Okay.

142
00:04:37,199 --> 00:04:38,120
Let me tell you,

143
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,759
I'm swamped here these days.

144
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:41,360
Once folks found out it's your shop,

145
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,639
they all rushed over for noodles.

146
00:04:43,079 --> 00:04:43,519
Sometimes,

147
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:44,759
the lunchtime line

148
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:46,000
stretches all the way to 4 p.m.

149
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,319
Isn't that a good thing?

150
00:04:48,839 --> 00:04:50,600
Some people drive all the way

151
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,519
from Shanghai

152
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:52,680
just for a bowl of my noodles.

153
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:54,439
I've been thinking,

154
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,399
maybe I should hire someone

155
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:56,160
to help out.

156
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:00,759
That's all thanks to the fans' passion.

157
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,319
You've been working so hard.

158
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:07,560
We should have a drink tonight.

159
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,160
We only got a 0-0 draw,

160
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:12,879
and you want to celebrate?

161
00:05:13,399 --> 00:05:14,279
When did we

162
00:05:14,519 --> 00:05:15,680
sink this low?

163
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:17,160
I've noticed, Chang Yi,

164
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:17,759
after all these years,

165
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,879
you haven't changed one bit.

166
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:20,360
That head of yours

167
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,120
has nothing in it

168
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,319
except football.

169
00:05:24,439 --> 00:05:26,000
So what day is today?

170
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,160
Our wedding anniversary.

171
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,160
And you didn't get me a gift.

172
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:39,360
Right, a gift.

173
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,120
What's this?

174
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:45,519
Right here.

175
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:47,879
Love you.

176
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:49,800
What's gotten into you lately?

177
00:05:52,519 --> 00:05:53,600
Um, well, I...

178
00:05:54,199 --> 00:05:55,639
Let's head to the back kitchen.

179
00:06:01,519 --> 00:06:02,720
Happy anniversary.

180
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,560
Once the season's over,

181
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,040
I'll make it up with a big gift.

182
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,399
Really?

183
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,319
Of course.

184
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:01,199
Son,

185
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:03,560
by the time you see

186
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,000
this footage,

187
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,839
Daddy might

188
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,680
not be around anymore.

189
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:11,399
My biggest wish

190
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:13,560
is for you

191
00:07:14,319 --> 00:07:15,360
to live a happy life.

192
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,240
And if you can,

193
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:20,160
I hope you'll fulfill my dream for me.

194
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,199
Daddy loves you forever.

195
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,199
Xiaoyong.

196
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,959
Pack up quick, time to go.

197
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:57,160
Buddha, please bless Changzhou FC.

198
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:59,800
Buddha, please don't listen to

199
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,639
those two next to me.

200
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:02,639
Buddha, please let Changzhou FC win.

201
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,879
Buddha, please bless us

202
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:04,720
with just one goal for Changzhou FC.

203
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:06,680
Buddha, please bless Changzhou FC.

204
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,240
Changzhou FC, with zero goals scored,

205
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,560
and Zhenjiang Team, on a seven-game losing streak,

206
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,839
are currently sitting dead last

207
00:08:12,839 --> 00:08:13,639
and second to last.

208
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,759
Truly partners in misery.

209
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,040
This is also Changzhou FC's

210
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:18,000
only possible shot at a win.

211
00:08:18,319 --> 00:08:19,000
Can the "Perpetual Last Place"

212
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,439
break the curse today?

213
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:21,439
Let's listen to

214
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:23,199
the cheers from the fans' section.

215
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,800
Changzhou must win!

216
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:31,920
Changzhou,

217
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:33,799
go!

218
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:35,799
Changzhou,

219
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:37,720
go!

220
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,000
Changzhou must win!

221
00:09:09,759 --> 00:09:11,200
Changzhou must win!

222
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:50,080
Goal!

223
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:51,559
Goal!

224
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,519
Goal!

225
00:09:59,279 --> 00:10:00,360
Mighty Changzhou!

226
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:08,039
After the match,

227
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,919
have Xiaoyong come over to the house.

228
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:22,720
Well done!

229
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:45,679
Hello.

230
00:10:45,799 --> 00:10:47,080
I'm Lü Qingqing, a reporter.

231
00:10:47,399 --> 00:10:48,080
We're working on a story

232
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,639
about our Changzhou FC.

233
00:11:02,799 --> 00:11:05,080
Everyone who refuses to give up at rock bottom

234
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:08,120
is writing their own Hero story.

235
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,200
Rather than waiting for the right moment,

236
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,200
it's better to be on the training ground,

237
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,399
inch by inch,

238
00:11:14,519 --> 00:11:15,679
carving out a path forward.

239
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,519
It's the sum of countless ordinary days and nights

240
00:11:18,759 --> 00:11:20,879
of gritting your teeth and pushing on.

241
00:11:23,519 --> 00:11:24,519
When referees make bad calls,

242
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:25,679
when injuries strike,

243
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,120
the cheers in the stadium

244
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:29,320
never fade away.

245
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,440
It shows how understanding

246
00:11:31,639 --> 00:11:33,720
has the power to cross mountains and seas.

247
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,559
Players and fans

248
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:48,120
grow together through their tears.

249
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,799
The football rolling across the grass

250
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,200
is really rolling over

251
00:11:52,559 --> 00:11:54,720
the humanity that sticks through thick and thin.

252
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,919
What if we lose again?

253
00:12:02,759 --> 00:12:03,679
To be honest,

254
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,000
this match of ours

255
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,360
really was pretty rough.

256
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:07,519
But

257
00:12:07,919 --> 00:12:08,639
right now, winning or losing

258
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:09,639
in the hearts of us fans

259
00:12:09,639 --> 00:12:10,879
is no longer the most important thing.

260
00:12:11,879 --> 00:12:12,360
It's...

261
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:14,759
it's our players on the pitch,

262
00:12:14,759 --> 00:12:16,159
their fighting spirit,

263
00:12:16,759 --> 00:12:17,679
that is what us fans

264
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,200
really want to see.

265
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,200
Even though our players'

266
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,000
battle is over,

267
00:12:22,639 --> 00:12:24,120
our fans' battle

268
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:24,960
isn't over yet.

269
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,559
On the pitch or off it,

270
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:28,919
we'll keep

271
00:12:28,919 --> 00:12:30,240
cheering on Changzhou FC.

272
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:31,879
I want to say

273
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:33,399
I want to tell Changzhou FC,

274
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,639
Changzhou FC,

275
00:12:35,639 --> 00:12:36,600
Win or lose,

276
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:37,679
we love you.

277
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:38,919
As long as you fight,

278
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,120
keep battling on.

279
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:50,919
Sometimes life's just like that.

280
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,279
You give it everything,

281
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:53,799
and it still falls short.

282
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,519
A lot of people say

283
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:56,440
our Changzhou FC,

284
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:58,200
compared to their squad,

285
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,440
look like farmers with hoes.

286
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,559
But I firmly believe

287
00:13:02,879 --> 00:13:05,440
our day of victory will come.

288
00:13:27,519 --> 00:13:28,360
Look, look, look!

289
00:13:28,799 --> 00:13:29,519
It's a close-up of you!

290
00:13:31,919 --> 00:13:32,320
Bro,

291
00:13:32,559 --> 00:13:33,000
check it out.

292
00:13:33,519 --> 00:13:34,679
I came across this too.

293
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:36,840
Gotta say, you're pretty photogenic.

294
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:40,600
This fan's got serious skills.

295
00:13:41,039 --> 00:13:41,639
Today,

296
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,559
after we played Zhenjiang Team,

297
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,080
our Changzhou

298
00:13:46,279 --> 00:13:47,200
felt like New Year's.

299
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:47,799
Yeah.

300
00:13:48,519 --> 00:13:50,039
When the bus came back,

301
00:13:50,679 --> 00:13:51,320
what a scene!

302
00:13:51,559 --> 00:13:52,720
Look, this fan's crying.

303
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,440
If I'd been there, I'd have cried too.

304
00:14:38,399 --> 00:14:40,000
We scored! That's amazing!

305
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:42,519
Brother!

306
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:43,440
No...

307
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,799
Let Xiaoyong speak first.

308
00:14:45,559 --> 00:14:46,440
Come on, sit down, sit down.

309
00:14:46,639 --> 00:14:47,960
Sit! Our Hero's back!

310
00:14:48,039 --> 00:14:48,879
Sit down, sit.

311
00:14:49,919 --> 00:14:51,360
I was just watching the replay of your match.

312
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:52,840
Fantastic, just fantastic!

313
00:14:52,879 --> 00:14:53,879
Here, have some water.

314
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,000
Let me tell you,

315
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,840
what's most admirable about you guys is

316
00:14:57,559 --> 00:14:58,440
you really showed

317
00:14:58,799 --> 00:15:00,679
that spirit of us Changzhou lads,

318
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,519
never giving up,

319
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:03,320
that perseverance.

320
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,200
You have no idea,

321
00:15:05,399 --> 00:15:06,440
your dad was watching at home

322
00:15:06,519 --> 00:15:07,639
and got so worked up.

323
00:15:07,679 --> 00:15:08,679
I wanted to jump in myself!

324
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:09,799
Dad,

325
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,960
that wasn't your attitude before.

326
00:15:12,159 --> 00:15:13,799
Well, I hadn't seen it before, had I?

327
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,080
I hadn't seen Xiaoyong's

328
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:17,159
brilliance on the green pitch.

329
00:15:19,679 --> 00:15:20,440
In one go,

330
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:21,919
two goals!

331
00:15:22,399 --> 00:15:23,399
One was an own goal,

332
00:15:23,519 --> 00:15:23,919
but still,

333
00:15:24,159 --> 00:15:25,399
it counts for our Changzhou FC.

334
00:15:26,279 --> 00:15:27,720
You kids had it so rough.

335
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:28,960
Listen, Xiaoyong,

336
00:15:29,879 --> 00:15:30,879
as long as you have this drive,

337
00:15:31,159 --> 00:15:31,799
in the future,

338
00:15:32,159 --> 00:15:33,559
you'll do well at anything.

339
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,519
How you play shows who you are.

340
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,639
If you want to play football,

341
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:39,679
go play with peace of mind.

342
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:40,679
Focus on your game.

343
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:41,879
As for everything else,

344
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:42,879
leave it to me.

345
00:15:44,679 --> 00:15:45,759
Now that I'm with Yaoyao,

346
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:47,759
I promise

347
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:48,679
I'll treat her well.

348
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:49,679
I believe you.

349
00:15:50,519 --> 00:15:50,840
That's wonderful.

350
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:51,919
Your aunt and I both believe in you.

351
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:54,200
Auntie made a whole table of food.

352
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,960
Today, let's skip the drinks.

353
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,679
Let's just enjoy a good meal together.

354
00:15:57,799 --> 00:15:58,799
Cheers! Come on, come on.

355
00:15:58,840 --> 00:15:59,360
Here we go.

356
00:15:59,639 --> 00:16:01,240
Hoping for even greater success from you.
